Package com.guardsquare.dexguard.runtime.encryption

Class EncryptedCordovaWebViewClient

java.lang.Object
android.webkit.WebViewClient
org.apache.cordova.CordovaWebViewClient
com.guardsquare.dexguard.runtime.encryption.EncryptedCordovaWebViewClient
public class EncryptedCordovaWebViewClient extends org.apache.cordova.CordovaWebViewClient
Deprecated.
EncryptedCordovaWebViewClient should only be used with old Cordova releases (< Cordova 4.0). When integrating newer Cordova releases, use EncryptedSystemWebViewClient instead.
This Cordova web view client can decrypt assets on the fly.

      Deprecated.
      Creates a new EncryptedCordovaWebViewClient.
      Parameters:
      delegate - the Cordova web view client to which all method invocations will be delegated.
      cordovaInterface - the Cordova interface that can provide the activity.
      encryptedAssetPrefix - a magic prefix value by which the assets to be decrypted can be recognized.
      assetInputStreamFactory - the input stream factory that can decrypt the assets.
